Package ie.atu.sw

Class FileProcessor

java.lang.Object
ie.atu.sw.FileProcessor
public class FileProcessor extends Object
Since:
1.8 Class FileProcessor contain methods that check the paths of the files, or select the default paths if non is selected by the user. It contain 3 methods, each one is responsible for different file path.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Tomasz Touma
